435
00:20:27,060 --> 00:20:28,490
You don't have to take it to heart.

436
00:20:28,580 --> 00:20:29,920
I can explain for you.

437
00:20:30,020 --> 00:20:31,050
Just let me go, okay?

438
00:20:31,140 --> 00:20:32,920
