512
00:25:35,430 --> 00:25:36,530
I like him.

513
00:25:38,380 --> 00:25:39,960
I thought you liked him too.

514
00:25:42,410 --> 00:25:43,790
I didn't lie on purpose.

515
00:25:46,450 --> 00:25:47,870
I know.

516
